ris Olympics\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Years of sacrifice, multiple fights and several breakdowns led to their big moment on May 27, when the duo's entry to the July 26-Aug 11 Games was confirmed by the Badminton World Federation (BWF).\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 816, \"end\": 842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Badminton_World_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Badminton World Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Badminton_World_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Badminton_World_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sacrifice\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 670}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple fights\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"several breakdowns\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"their big moment\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"the duo's entry\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 766}, {\"ngram\": \"-Aug\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"BWF\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This makes them Singapore's first local-born mixed doubles duo to qualify for the Olympics - Indonesia-born Hendri Saputra and China-born Li Yujia were the first from the Republic to feature in the event at Beijing 2008.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 959, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendri_Saputra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hendri Saputra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendri_Saputra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hendri_Saputra\"}, {\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Yujia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Li Yujia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Yujia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li_Yujia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Republic\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"Beijing\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The married couple have been on edge after a topsy-turvy qualifying campaign, with the spot determined by Australia's decision on which events to use their continental quotas.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8001791290904745, \"rank\": 0.18617608860830304, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The married couple\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"edge\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"a topsy-turvy qualifying campaign\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"the spot\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"their continental quotas\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Insisting that they deserved to go through, Hee, 28, admitted to monitoring the rankings almost obsessively at one stage.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hee\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"the rankings\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"one stage\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I do not believe we were lucky because we put in a lot of work and effort to put ourselves in that position to take up the slot which Australia freed up.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1516, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re