, {\"sentence\": \"Tan said: \\\"There was anxiety for sure.\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tan\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we fell out of the top 13, there were so few tournaments to catch up after that, so the pressure became mountain high and we struggled.\\\"\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so few tournaments\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3138}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The duo's entry to the July 26-Aug 11 Paris Games was confirmed by the Badminton World Federation on May 27.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3291, \"end\": 3317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Badminton_World_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Badminton World Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Badminton_World_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Badminton_World_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The duo's entry\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"-Aug\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ST PHOTO: AZMI ATHNI But the world No.\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ST PHOTO\", \"from\": 3330, \"to\": 3338}, {\"ngram\": \"AZMI ATHNI\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"But the world No\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"17 pair received a lifeline as Australia, which had qualified in four events, elected to take up the slots in the women's singles and women's doubles.\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3401, \"end\": 3410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.8001791290904745, \"rank\": 0.18617608860830304, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"17 pair\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifeline\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3397}, {\"ngram\": \"four events\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3446}, {\"ngram\": \"the slots\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3476}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's singles\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"women's doubles\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This freed up one more mixed doubles spot for the next eligible pair in the rankings, which went to the Singaporeans.\", \"from\": 3521, \"to\": 3638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3625, \"end\": 3637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0725372692183415e-18, \"text\": \"Singaporeans\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singaporeans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one more mixed doubles spot\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3562}, {\"ngram\": \"the next eligible pair\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3589}, {\"ngram\": \"the rankings\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Besides sweating over their ranking, their Olympic quest has been a roller-coaster ride.\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their ranking\", \"from\": 3662, \"to\": 3675}, {\"ngram\": \"their Olympic quest\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3696}, {\"ngram\": \"a roller-coaster ride\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since becoming a mixed doubles pair in 2014, they have had to work through Hee's national service commitments and Tan's shoulder and knee surgeries - their world ranking slipped from a high of 15th in 2017 to 808th a year later.\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a mixed doubles pair\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3765}, {\"ngram\": \"Hee's national service commitments\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"Tan's shoulder\", \"from\": 3844, \"to\": 3858}, {\"ngram\": \"knee surgeries\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3877}, {\"ngram\": \"their world ranking\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 3899}, {\"ngram\": \"a high\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3919}, {\"ngram\": \"15th\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They bounced back after they got married in October 2021 and have since won six titles, including the historic 2022 Commonwealth Games gold.\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 4100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"six titles\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4046}, {\"ngram\": \"the historic 2022 Commonwealth Games gold\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were other challenges, as Hee made the difficult decision to end a promising men's doubles partnership with Loh Kean Hean at the end of 2022 to focus on mixed doubles, while Tan's mother died from illness a few months later.\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4216, \"end\": 4229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loh_Kean_Hean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Loh Kean Hean\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loh_Kean_Hean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loh_Kean_Hean\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other challenges\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"Hee\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4137}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficult decision\", \"from\": 4143, \"to\": 4165}, {\"ngram\": \"a promising men's doubles partnership\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4210}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 4233, \"to\": 4240}, {\"ngram\": \"mixed doubles\", \"from\": 4261, \"to\": 4274}, {\"ngram\": \"Tan's mother\", \"from\": 4282, \"to\": 4294}, {\"ngram\": \"illness\", \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tan said: \\\"It was very hard for me to take, and I felt very guilty about not spending more time with my mother because we had to travel a lot for competitions.\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tan\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4337}, {\"ngram\": \"more time\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4429}, {\"ngram\": \"my mother\", \"from\": 4435, \"to\": 4444}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4470, \"to\": 4475}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 4480, \"to\": 4492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then, we kept getting knocked out in the first round, which was a hit to our Olympic dreams, and I was in a very bad place because I felt I dragged us down with my personal issues.\\\"\", \"from\": 4495, \"to\": 4677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"a hit\", \"from\": 4560, \"to\": 4565}, {\"ngram\": \"our Olympic dreams\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4587}, {\"ngram\": \"a very bad place\", \"from\": 4602, \"to\": 4618}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4644, \"to\": 4646}, {\"ngram\": \"my personal issues\", \"from\": 4657, \"to\": 4675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Squabbles ensued during their slump, and the couple credited national doubles coach Paulus Firman for being \\\"a coach, mentor, mediator and father figure\\\".\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4763, \"end\": 4769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9999999842020771, \"rank\": 1.5790163849504348e-08, \"text\": \"Paulus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 4770, \"end\": 4776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Firman\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.67355849638305e-13, \"text\": \"Firman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Firman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Firman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Squabbles\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4688}, {\"ngram\": \"their slump\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4714}, {\"ngram\": \"the couple\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4730}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4795}, {\"ngram\": \"mentor\", \"from\": 4797, \"to\": 4803}, {\"ngram\": \"mediator\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4813}, {\"ngram\": \"father figure\", \"from\": 4818, \"to\": 4831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paulus said: \\\"Sometimes scolding is required, but there are times when I give advice and invite them to discuss and find a solution.\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paulus\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 4895, \"to\": 4900}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 4913, \"to\": 4919}, {\"ngram\": \"a solution\", \"from\": 4956, \"to\": 4966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also share my experiences with them on how to face and resolve problems, especially since they are both athletes and husband and wife.\\\"\", \"from\": 4968, \"to\": 5105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my experiences\", \"from\": 4981, \"to\": 4995}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 5033, \"to\": 5041}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 5074, \"to\": 5082}, {\"ngram\": \"husband\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5094}, {\"ngram\": \"wife\", \"from\": 5099, \"to\": 5103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A deadpan Hee then shared how his wife would \\\"bring out a plate of grapes\\\" at home after quarrels, though a smiling Tan refuted this by adding \\\"true story, but in reverse\\\".\", \"from\": 5107, \"to\": 5279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A deadpan\", \"from\": 5107, \"to\": 5116}, {\"ngram\": \"Hee\", \"from\": 5117, \"to\": 5120}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5145}, {\"ngram\": \"a plate\", \"from\": 5163, \"to\": 5170}, {\"ngram\": \"grapes\", \"from\": 5174, \"to\": 5180}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 5185, \"to\": 5189}, {\"ngram\": \"quarrels\", \"from\": 5196, \"to\": 5204}, {\"ngram\": \"a smiling Tan\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5226}, {\"ngram\": \"true story\", \"from\": 5251, \"to\": 5261}, {\"ngram\": \"reverse\", \"from\": 5270, \"to\": 5277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will be looking to savour the fruits of their labour at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5281, \"to\": 5355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fruits\", \"from\": 5312, \"to\": 5322}, {\"ngram\": \"their labour\", \"from\": 5326, \"to\": 5338}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5342, \"to\": 5354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hee said: \\\"Through our fights, we learnt more about ourselves and each other.\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hee\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5360}, {\"ngram\": \"our fights\", \"from\": 5376, \"to\": 5386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have gone through that, and grown in terms of mentality, understanding and individual ability.\", \"from\": 5435, \"to\": 5532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 5475, \"to\": 5480}, {\"ngram\": \"mentality\", \"from\": 5484, \"to\": 5493}, {\"ngram\": \"understanding\", \"from\": 5495, \"to\": 5508}, {\"ngram\": \"individual ability\", \"from\": 5513, \"to\": 5531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are a better team than ever before, and there are always upsets at the Olympics because the pressure is on the higher-ranked teams not to lose.\\\"\", \"from\": 5533, \"to\": 5680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better team\", \"from\": 5540, \"to\": 5553}, {\"ngram\": \"upsets\", \"from\": 5593, \"to\": 5599}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5615}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5636}, {\"ngram\": \"the higher-ranked teams\", \"from\": 5643, \